OL,6,FIn statement released on Friday, Chief
OL,7,FInspector Vicks Hayward-Melen said:
OL,8,F"The loss of such young children, who
OL,9,Fhad their whole lives ahead of them,
OL,10,Fis truly heartbreaking and our
OL,11,Fthoughts remain with their family and
OL,12,Feveryone affected by this tragedy.
OL,14,F"Our specialist liaison officers will
OL,15,Fcontinue to provide their next of kin
OL,16,Fwith any help and support they need.
