OL,6,F"Over the past few days, forensic post-
OL,7,Fmortem examinations have been carried
OL,8,Fout on the children. We can now
OL,9,Fconfirm the cause of death for each
OL,10,Fchild was knife injuries.
OL,12,F"A 42-year-old woman arrested on
OL,13,Fsuspicion of their murder remains in
OL,14,Fhospital undergoing treatment for non
OL,15,Flife-threatening injuries."
OL,17,FThe investigation into the incident is
OL,18,F"progressing at pace", the force added.
OL,20,FA vigil is due to be held later today
OL,21,Fin memory of the children.
